"pid":"efd5ee3e6a40fe2db2a2c0e88a60e286b40f4ffc","tid":1308863,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拮野家就拮野家啦，扑野咁粗俗！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n香港吉野家強姦案於2008年4月發生，並在同年9月開始受到傳媒廣泛報導，網絡上更流傳一段用手機拍攝的強姦短片。短片中的兩男一女均身穿吉野家餐廳的員工制服，女方疑遭兩名男同事強暴。短片長約1分48秒，大小約1,854千字節，清晰地拍下受害女子以及兩名男子的樣貌，並錄下受害女子說要報警求助的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n該短片在2008年8月下旬開始，透過手機極速流傳。自報章揭發此事後，警方根據短片內容進行調查，並在同年9月10日拘捕3名懷疑涉案人士。同時，該短片開始被網民傳送入電腦，再透過網絡急速傳至全港，並在翌日出現約萬多個來源，增長程度非常驚人，令強姦事件震驚全港。有關短片快速傳至中國大陸、澳門及台灣等地，該次事件與「藝人床照流出事件」有相似之處。<br />\n</span><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f10fae8438aa804227bf71f993160860fdc98ac0","tid":1308863,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01507d77b0539192a028640dc0796443891a439e","tid":1308863,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拮野家就拮野家啦，扑野咁粗俗！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"調撚準未"},{"pid":"7f4d870b0a494d9fd963b3be86519caf2d77db94","tid":1308863,"uid":233705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:25:53.000Z","msg":"條撚準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ced19eaae274e3396bfdc606dc06045df3fdf2","tid":1308863,"uid":164368,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"314d1ec0003e5d686059b262d23926a23b15a7d4","tid":1308863,"uid":25382,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"罷食算啦<br />\n玩9前線職員有咩意思<img src=\"/a